snippet: The two-time Australian Open champion Victoria Azarenka wasted two match points in the second set before falling to Karolina Pliskova of the Czech Republic.
abstract: Karolina Pliskova of the Czech Republic rallies to a first-round win over Victoria Azarenka in Brisbane International in Australia; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: The two-time Australian Open champion Victoria Azarenka wasted two match points in the second set before falling to Karolina Pliskova of the Czech Republic.

headline.main: Azarenka Loses in First Round at Brisbane
